**Keyboard Shortcuts:**
• G: Grid view
• D: Develop module
• E: Loupe view
• P: Flag as pick
• X: Reject
• Numbers: Apply star ratings

**Collections:**
• Smart collections for quick access
• Project-based collections
• "To Edit" and "Done" collections
