• Non-destructive adjustments
• Return to Lightroom
• Maintain catalog organization

### Color Management

**Calibration:**
• Monitor calibration (monthly)
• Color checker for camera profile
• Consistent viewing conditions
• Proof colors for print

**Color Spaces:**
• sRGB: Web, social media, most screens
• Adobe RGB: Wider gamut, print
• ProPhoto RGB: Maximum range, archival

### Backup Strategy

**3-2-1 Rule:**
• 3 copies of data
• 2 different media types
• 1 off-site backup

**Implementation:**
• Working drive (fast SSD)
• Backup drive (external HDD)
• Cloud storage (Backblaze, Google Drive)

**Frequency:**
• Daily for current projects
• Weekly for archives
• Immediate for critical work

### Time Management

**Realistic Estimates:**
• Wedding: 20-30 hours editing
• Portrait session: 2-4 hours
• Commercial product: 1-2 hours per image

**Efficiency Gains:**
