• Develop reusable presets
• Keyboard shortcuts mastery
• Streamlined decision-making

### Quality Control Checklist

**Before Delivery:**
□ Consistent exposure across set
□ Accurate colors
□ No dust spots or artifacts
□ Proper sharpening applied
□ Straight horizons/verticals
□ Consistent editing style
□ Correct resolution/format
□ Organized and labeled

### Client Delivery

**Gallery Options:**
• Pixieset, ShootProof, SmugMug
• Password protection
• Download options
• Print ordering integration

**Delivery Timeline:**
• Set clear expectations
• Communicate progress
• Meet deadlines consistently
• Provide tracking information

### Advanced Techniques

**Frequency Separation:**
• Separate texture and color
• Professional skin retouching
• Preserve detail while smoothing

**Luminosity Masks:**
• Precise tonal adjustments
• Non-destructive editing
• Professional grade control

**Color Grading:**
• Develop signature look
• Mood enhancement
• Brand consistency

